{
  "stem": "27347.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She saw me on a daily basis.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She used to say such wonderful things to me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We-- I could never do anything wrong when she was around.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "No one would hit me or touch me or scream at me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was always protected.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She used to say, 'When I look at you, [GERMAN].' That was such a silly thing, but everything from the past is so dear.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And even silly little things mean so much because it was a beautiful life, it was wiped out, it never happen again, it will never--",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was very independent.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She lived alone.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She visited most of her children on a daily basis.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was very energetic.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "To get around in Vienna, it was not next door, but she made sure that all her children are OK.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she was sort of a Robin Hood, because if some of her children had more money than the others, she'd try to equalize it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She tried to touch their conscience that their brother needs help or something.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That I remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she always told me that wealth means nothing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "If you can't share it, if you see someone suffer, then you really cannot be happy with your money or anything.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My grandfather I never met because he died when my mother was seven months old.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's how they got to Vienna, because my mother was born in Lemberg, Lwow, in Poland.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My grandmother had seven children.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She-- after her husband passed away, she packed up, came to Vienna, and had all her children educated.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was easier for her to provide for her children.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she organized women and she was making shirts, sewing shirts, men's shirts, and selling them to stores, and she educated all her children.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
